ed="B" n="0188a12"/><anchor n="B.27.0151.0188a12"/><head>清四明天童寺沙門釋通容傳</head><lb
ed="B" n="0188a13"/><p xml:id="pB27p0188a1301"><persName key="A001150">釋通容</persName>，字<persName key="A001150">費隱</persName>，姓<name>何</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000017495">福清</placeName>人。幼孤，叔父送之鎮東衛依<persName key="A003827">慧山</persName><lb
ed="B" n="0188a14"/>出家，<ref type="date" target="#j23076772308031">年已十四</ref>矣！初參<persName key="A003828">壽昌經</persName>有省，後參<persName key="A000114">博山來</persName>、<persName key="A005648">顯聖澄</persName>俱以<lb
ed="B" n="0188a15"/>法器目之。依<persName key="A005648">澄</persName>最久，常命代座說法。自謂：「<ref type="person" target="#A001150">吾</ref>斯未信，痛念大事<lb
ed="B" n="0188a16"/>因緣。」不覺流涕。閱《<persName key="A003688">密雲<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>語錄》，傾心嚮慕，往謁於<placeName key="PL000000013252">越</placeName>之<placeName key="PL000000013194">吼山</placeName><lb
ed="B" n="0188a17"/>寓次<!-- 參g086p0115 -->。橫機不讓，<persName key="A003688">密</persName>唯痛棒，頭腦幾裂。一時知見，猛然頓釋。自是<lb
ed="B" n="0188a18"/>隨侍，通玄<persName key="A000490">黃檗</persName>，益入閫奧。受屬後隨住<placeName key="PL000000017360">黃檗</placeName>，旋之<placeName key="PL000000012794">金粟</placeName>。未幾又<lb
ed="B" n="0188a19"/>遷<placeName key="PL000000012319">天童</placeName>，清理南山墖院，恢復<placeName>東谷</placeName>，贖還侵田三百餘畝。方<persName key="A001150">容</persName>之<lb
ed="B" n="0188a20"/>初入院也，徧謁祖塔，扶杖過<placeName>東谷</placeName>，見塔宇刊落，影堂淪墟，荒碑<pb ed="B" xml:id="B27.0151.0188b" n="0188b"/><lb
ed="B" n="0188b01"/>殘碣，偃臥階戺<!-- 門檻 -->間。皆先師銘詞、香積田數，紀載詳盡，文旨斐然。<lb
ed="B" n="0188b02"/>嘗有居民擬操巨斧，擊仆<date from-iso="+1127-06-19" key="j21328572188290" to-iso="+1279-03-26"><name>宋</name></date><persName key="A007177">周<roleName>益公</roleName></persName>碑銘不中，反中其首，因病<lb
ed="B" n="0188b03"/>創死。<persName key="A001150">容</persName>衋然<!-- 傷痛 -->傷之。未幾，得<persName key="A042492">孫<roleName>觀察</roleName>子秀</persName>、<persName key="A015600">張<roleName>大將軍</roleName>杰</persName>、<persName key="A042491">吳<roleName>參戎</roleName>岱</persName><lb
ed="B" n="0188b04"/>為之計匡復，闢荊榛、摧井竈，草薙而禽獼<!-- 如同割除野草，捕殺禽獸一般。 -->之，並按碑問諸侵蝕<lb
ed="B" n="0188b05"/>法產者。於是<placeName key="PL000000012319">太白</placeName>之陰，<persName key="A004721">寶藏</persName>之林，<persName key="A003799">興</persName><persName key="A042493">璿</persName>之英，七十二祖之靈無<lb
ed="B" n="0188b06"/>復卷婁<!-- 駝背俛曲 -->之垢藏，甌寠<!-- 狹小的高地 -->之曼聲<!-- 舒緩的長聲。參g012p0131黃承昊：天童興復東谷記 -->。至今論繼述功，於<persName key="A001150">容</persName>稱最。後主<placeName key="PL000000011848">徑<lb
ed="B" n="0188b07"/>山</placeName>，投老<!-- 臨老、告老 --><placeName key="PL000000012941">石門</placeName>之<placeName key="PL000000012913">福嚴</placeName>。<date when-iso="+1661-03-19" key="j23278062327806"><name>清</name><name>順治</name>辛丑二月十九日</date>示寂。逾數載始<lb
ed="B" n="0188b08"/>化，獲舍利無算，分供諸方。著有《語錄》二十卷。弟子<persName key="A016519">徹綱</persName><!-- 徹綱於堯峰容座下圓具。(CBETA, X82, no. 1571, p. 483, a3-4) -->從<persName key="A015600"><persName key="A042490">石劍<lb
ed="B" n="0188b09"/>常</persName>分得舍利子一，大如菽。歸<placeName key="PL000000034763">蜀昭覺</placeName>起窣堵波——於<persName key="A003688">圓悟</persName>之左，<persName key="A009652">破<lb
ed="B" n="0188b10"/>山</persName>之右。今猶鼎峙云。</p>
